result.name: The Sky Bar

reviews.text: It's a wonderful place for a lunch. You may have your choice of dish from a pasta, chicken stake, dish fillet, to beef and enjoy the vegetable salad bar unlimited. Hall is big in width and height, so you may feel calm and free. Staffs are serving in a nice and reasonable manner. All foods are prepared excellently. Coool !

Steak and lobster with the semi buffet dinner is good. The variety of salad and dessert is fair to its price. I booked a table for 5 with one wheelchair so they gave me a table for 6. The service is good as well. They have a buy 3 get 1 free discount for guest with birthday in the month. The suggested dining time was 90min but they allowed more time for us as no guests were waiting outside. A good place for a nice chat with drinks.
Food are good, salad bar is fair, value for oney
The food is good. But some of the ingredients of the salad bar has gone bad.
as the restaurant said, you can enjoy affordable deluxe dinning

reviews.text: 快餐感覺😕

It's a wonderful place for a lunch. You may have your choice of dish from a pasta, chicken stake, dish fillet, to beef and enjoy the vegetable salad bar unlimited. Hall is big in width and height, so you may feel calm and free. Staffs are serving in a nice and reasonable manner. All foods are prepared excellently. Coool !
平均百五至二百五消費，有個半自助輕食甜品吧，食物質素合理，唯隨餐只有一小杯冰茶，額外飲品要加錢，很怪的安排
環境不錯，食物味道好，自助沙拉同甜品正。
